subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description: The project will generate decent employment, particularly for young people and promote social cohesion through supporting the formulation and implementation of appropriate pro-poor policies, capacity strenghthening of relevant institutions and the creation of sustainable enterprises.
subproject.title: RAF/08/007- Youth Employment
